    "description": "💟ADD IN WISHLIST!!💟<br> <br><br><strong>《猫次郎》</strong>是一款结合打工模拟、养成收集的疗愈游戏。<br>结帐、补货、微波、清洁、霜淇淋制作，完成便利商店工作、获得报酬满足猫次郎的需求，一人一猫的暖心日常就此展开。&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/bf85d1ad6433c62ab7f8d301611c545d.poster.avif?t=1710319937\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/bf85d1ad6433c62ab7f8d301611c545d.webm?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/bf85d1ad6433c62ab7f8d301611c545d.mp4?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>成为万能便利商店店员！从达成顾客需求、赚取更多薪资开始！<br>根据工作难度、所需时间妥善安排时程，让顾客满意，顺利渡过忙碌期吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/9054d84f89d3221b0de7d6e47b9cabf3.poster.avif?t=1710319937\" width=600 height=530 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/9054d84f89d3221b0de7d6e47b9cabf3.webm?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/9054d84f89d3221b0de7d6e47b9cabf3.mp4?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/81e61df33662ae4262e668a7b1a0ad0f.poster.avif?t=1710319937\" width=574 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/81e61df33662ae4262e668a7b1a0ad0f.webm?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/81e61df33662ae4262e668a7b1a0ad0f.mp4?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>赚到薪水之后就拿来好好的献给猫次郎吧，猫次郎吃饱喝足之后好像会有一些特别的变化？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/f71cc582c1780648b3d95c22bb897faf.poster.avif?t=1710319937\" width=544 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/f71cc582c1780648b3d95c22bb897faf.webm?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/f71cc582c1780648b3d95c22bb897faf.mp4?t=1710319937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果猫次郎吃饱了但还有剩下的薪水，那就拿来添购新的家具和摆设，把自己家装潢的更加温馨吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/671253a311600ac0c9af969c23e86234.apng?t=1710319937\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157340/extras/671253a311600ac0c9af969c23e86234.poster.avif?t=1710319937\" class=\"bb_img\" width=648 height=378 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>各种便利商店工作项目小游戏玩法。<br></li><li>多样化的客人类型。<br></li><li>可爱的猫次郎。<br></li><li>可以拥有一个温馨的小窝。</li></ul>",
